    362          /**
    363           * Read the Maintain process parameters from the setting file and setup the Maintain process.
    364           * Determine the delay seconds and setup the condition displacement based on the referenced
    365           * setting file parameters. If a modifier exists, it is applied to the delay seconds.
    366           * @param control = Pointer to the process control parameters from the Interpreter.
    367           */

